<% content_for :exhibition do %>
  <div class="articleContainer">
    <div class="spacer">
      <div class="description">
        <article>
          <h1>Projects of <%= image_tag 'projectlodge-light.png', :alt => '.projectlodge',:class => 'projectlodgeLogo' %>?</h1>
          <div class="column">
            <p>The question should not be who, but what! TODO</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <p>Bla bla bla... we need more of this to make it interesting. Maybe some animations or a combined graph. Options we have, content we do not. This needs some love and attention.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="signUp">
        <h2>Come and join in.</h2>
        <p>Create a new account</p>
